  <div class="modal-header">
    <h3 class="title-small">Express interest in {{opening.name}}</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-text">
    <p>
      The Projects Board will send an email to the managers of the posting "{{opening.name}}" on your behalf, cc'ing you. The email will contain a link to your profile page, so make sure it looks good!
